      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer. Every surface and mechanical component has been preserved to an exacting standard, ensuring a driving experience that mirrors its original factory state. This is an investment-grade acquisition defined by its flawless aesthetic and peerless performance. Meticulously inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, it stands as a testament to superior automotive maintenance.",
